  <heading>BRK</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Breakpoint instruction</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>Breakpoint instruction. A <instruction>BRK</instruction> instruction generates a Breakpoint Instruction exception. The PE records the exception in <xref linkend="ESR_ELx">ESR_ELx</xref>, using the EC value <hexnumber>0x3c</hexnumber>, and captures the value of the immediate argument in <xref linkend="ESR_ELx">ESR_ELx</xref>.ISS.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
